{"tid":276843,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"［求教］脫墨之後要點護理？","createTime":"2017-06-09T06:30:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-09T07:45:00.000Z","uid":85644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4df2ea72b2f75318abb597c0af31f961aa666e34","tid":276843,"uid":85644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T06:30:55.000Z","msg":"琴日去咗脫墨 係用藥水脫嘅<br />\n脫之前個姨姨比咗佢客人嘅成果我睇<br />\n見到好大粒果d都脫到<br />\n所以我就脫咗面上面嘅三粒<br />\n想問下巴絲們 脫完之後要點樣護理？<br />\n可唔可以用水洗面？不過琴晚已經用咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n或者有咩特別注意<br />\n唔想有疤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"237346f42999bcc97d0a14f052d08f53dd93fa21","tid":276843,"uid":85644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T06:32:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c45da68612198827e4373f821b674d305d82bf88","tid":276843,"uid":85644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T06:32:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"79c060749df1f9590b0b5bc29dfe60d2e406fcab","tid":276843,"uid":85644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T06:33:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ff8fc4ab54ccac05419695dd001afe9b8af17188","tid":276843,"uid":85644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T06:36:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1e5a1dce698dedbfd456a1076694903e6ceb9a66","tid":276843,"uid":49782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T06:36:53.000Z","msg":"我用激光脫<br />\n冇護理 三個月後冇手尾跟冇印"},{"pid":"5b44a2e100ec572b8f3024109537aa39536e48d6","tid":276843,"uid":85644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T06:39:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我用激光脫<br />\n冇護理 三個月後冇手尾跟冇印</blockquote><br />\n洗面都照洗？google好多人話唔可以濕水"},{"pid":"2d59b8ab1583212656e7ebc614f2ffc58985392d","tid":276843,"uid":65429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T06:41:22.000Z","msg":"唔好用水侯水洗<br />\n唔好食咁多蛋類同士油"},{"pid":"4785145580ec5905c04399f6bb3e7a7011b420ec